{"article_id":"61oJ9qFcPtPyWWYG","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Cruz 's Methodical Delegate Strategy Narrows Trump 's Path To GOP Nomination","depth":1},{"id":1,"text":"On the way into the Colorado Republican Party 's state convention in Colorado Springs Saturday morning , a Ted Cruz supporter waved a big broom with the letters `` CRUZ ''","depth":10},{"id":2,"text":"fastened to the top .","depth":10},{"id":3,"text":"The convention took place in a hockey arena ,","depth":10},{"id":4,"text":"and the prop is probably familiar to most sports fans .","depth":10},{"id":5,"text":"The Cruz supporter was looking for a sweep ,","depth":10},{"id":6,"text":"and a sweep was what he got .","depth":10},{"id":7,"text":"Cruz picked up all 34 Republican National Convention delegates","depth":11},{"id":8,"text":"that Colorado Republicans awarded this week .","depth":11},{"id":9,"text":"Delegates","depth":12},{"id":10,"text":"backing Cruz","depth":12},{"id":11,"text":"won all three spots in each of the state 's seven congressional districts , as well as 13 statewide slots .","depth":11},{"id":12,"text":"The Colorado win follows a similar outcome in North Dakota ,","depth":8},{"id":13,"text":"where Republicans elected a mostly Cruz-approved slate of delegates at a state convention last week .","depth":8},{"id":14,"text":"Those two delegate hauls , along with more complex delegate maneuvering in states like Louisiana","depth":8},{"id":15,"text":"that had already held their primaries and caucuses ,","depth":8},{"id":16,"text":"highlight a growing organizational gap between Cruz 's campaign and frontrunner Donald Trump 's .","depth":7},{"id":17,"text":"As recently as last month , the Cruz campaign insisted","depth":10},{"id":18,"text":"that he was fighting to win 1,237 delegates and clinch the GOP nomination outright ,","depth":10},{"id":19,"text":"though Cruz told the Denver Post on Saturday","depth":10},{"id":20,"text":"that a contested convention is a `` very significant possibility . ''","depth":10},{"id":21,"text":"Cruz also expressed confidence","depth":9},{"id":22,"text":"that he would win in such a scenario .","depth":9},{"id":23,"text":"The Texas senator has become the candidate of choice for many Republicans","depth":10},{"id":24,"text":"simply trying to stop Trump .","depth":10},{"id":25,"text":"Cruz 's organizational successes offer hope to them","depth":10},{"id":26,"text":"that he will succeed","depth":11},{"id":27,"text":"in blocking Trump 's path .","depth":11},{"id":28,"text":"Though many of them stop short of saying","depth":9},{"id":29,"text":"they 'd like Cruz to be the eventual nominee .","depth":9},{"id":30,"text":"Most political observers did n't figure","depth":11},{"id":31,"text":"Colorado would play a role in the Republican primary ,","depth":11},{"id":32,"text":"after the state declined to hold a binding primary or caucus .","depth":10},{"id":33,"text":"Still , Congressman Ken Buck ,","depth":12},{"id":34,"text":"who chairs Cruz 's Colorado campaign ,","depth":12},{"id":35,"text":"said ,","depth":11},{"id":36,"text":"`` dozens of volunteers have been working since December '' in Colorado","depth":11},{"id":37,"text":"to vet delegate candidates","depth":12},{"id":38,"text":"and organize at local caucuses and regional meetings .","depth":12},{"id":39,"text":"On Saturday morning , Cruz volunteers","depth":13},{"id":40,"text":"wearing bright orange shirts","depth":13},{"id":41,"text":"swept through the arena ,","depth":12},{"id":42,"text":"handing out glossy sheets","depth":12},{"id":43,"text":"listing the campaign 's preferred delegate candidates .","depth":12},{"id":44,"text":"The campaign also blasted out text messages to convention attendees ,","depth":11},{"id":45,"text":"listing their delegate choices .","depth":11},{"id":46,"text":"`` We put 15 delegate","depth":14},{"id":47,"text":"[ candidates ]","depth":14},{"id":48,"text":"forward , ''","depth":13},{"id":49,"text":"said Buck ,","depth":13},{"id":50,"text":"who won a spot as a delegate himself .","depth":13},{"id":51,"text":"`` We looked at people","depth":13},{"id":52,"text":"that had run","depth":14},{"id":53,"text":"and won in the past .","depth":14},{"id":54,"text":"We looked at people","depth":14},{"id":55,"text":"who had been supporting Cruz for a long time .","depth":14},{"id":56,"text":"We looked at elected officials","depth":14},{"id":57,"text":"who knew how to run campaigns . ''","depth":14},{"id":58,"text":"That organizational effort was a stark contrast to Trump 's campaign ,","depth":11},{"id":59,"text":"which only had a handful of volunteers","depth":12},{"id":60,"text":"distributing delegate candidate lists .","depth":12},{"id":61,"text":"The Trump slate was riddled with errors .","depth":9},{"id":62,"text":"According to NBC News ,","depth":11},{"id":63,"text":"the Trump campaign failed to put forward a candidate slate in some of the earlier district-level contests .","depth":11},{"id":64,"text":"In another congressional district , two of the candidates","depth":12},{"id":65,"text":"they urged voters to back","depth":12},{"id":66,"text":"did not , in fact , make it onto the ballot .","depth":11},{"id":67,"text":"`` What this says for the Trump campaign is ,","depth":11},{"id":68,"text":"you need to get your stuff in gear , ''","depth":11},{"id":69,"text":"said former Republican National Committee Chairman Michael Steele .","depth":10},{"id":70,"text":"`` Because you 're about to get your clock cleaned on the easy stuff .","depth":10},{"id":71,"text":"A lot of folks","depth":12},{"id":72,"text":"look at ,","depth":13},{"id":73,"text":"we just won the primary .","depth":13},{"id":74,"text":"The is n't about just winning the primary .","depth":13},{"id":75,"text":"It 's about winning delegates .","depth":13},{"id":76,"text":"You get your delegates","depth":13},{"id":77,"text":"wherever and however you can . ''","depth":13},{"id":78,"text":"Indeed , the Trump campaign has made changes in recent days ,","depth":7},{"id":79,"text":"bringing in longtime Washington operative Paul Manafort","depth":8},{"id":80,"text":"to play a role in convention preparation , as well as broader campaign strategy .","depth":8},{"id":81,"text":"Manafort was asked about the result in Colorado on NBC 's Meet The Press on Sunday","depth":8},{"id":82,"text":"and responded ,","depth":9},{"id":83,"text":"`` I acknowledge","depth":10},{"id":84,"text":"that we were n't playing in Colorado","depth":11},{"id":85,"text":"and they did . ''","depth":11},{"id":86,"text":"He went on to criticize the pro-Cruz efforts as too aggressive ,","depth":8},{"id":87,"text":"making an accusation of `` Gestapo tactics '' in various local party conventions .","depth":8},{"id":88,"text":"Steele praised the Cruz campaign 's organizational efforts ,","depth":8},{"id":89,"text":"but cautioned","depth":10},{"id":90,"text":"against reading too much into the Colorado and North Dakota convention victories","depth":11},{"id":91,"text":"when looking forward to a possible Cleveland floor fight .","depth":11},{"id":92,"text":"`` Going into a state","depth":12},{"id":93,"text":"and grabbing unbound delegates","depth":13},{"id":94,"text":"and getting commitments and all that is not the same","depth":13},{"id":95,"text":"as going into a convention hall","depth":12},{"id":96,"text":"where overlaying everything is the RNC rules , ''","depth":12},{"id":97,"text":"he said .","depth":10},{"id":98,"text":"Having a political and legal staff","depth":11},{"id":99,"text":"that understands the party 's regulations and guidelines","depth":11},{"id":100,"text":"are key ,","depth":10},{"id":101,"text":"he said ,","depth":9},{"id":102,"text":"giving the Cruz campaign the advantage on that front .","depth":8},{"id":103,"text":"But Steele argued","depth":7},{"id":104,"text":"that another important factor is , `` having delegates on the floor and relevant committees , ''","depth":10},{"id":105,"text":"Steele said ,","depth":10},{"id":106,"text":"primarily the Rules Committee ,","depth":10},{"id":107,"text":"which will shape the convention proceedings .","depth":10},{"id":108,"text":"`` The Trump team is going to be competitive on that front ,","depth":10},{"id":109,"text":"because they 've got a lot of delegates , and the ability","depth":11},{"id":110,"text":"to put their people on that committee","depth":12},{"id":111,"text":"and have weight on that committee , ''","depth":12},{"id":112,"text":"said Steele .","depth":9},{"id":113,"text":"Both campaigns will spend the next two months","depth":5},{"id":114,"text":"gearing up for a historic floor fight .","depth":5},{"id":115,"text":"That 's because","depth":5},{"id":116,"text":"while Trump may still secure the delegates","depth":7},{"id":117,"text":"he needs to avoid one ,","depth":7},{"id":118,"text":"there 's no chance","depth":7},{"id":119,"text":"he can do so until June 7 , the very last day of the primary calendar .","depth":7},{"id":120,"text":"Clarification :","depth":4},{"id":121,"text":"This post has been updated","depth":5},{"id":122,"text":"to reflect Cruz 's recent comments","depth":6},{"id":123,"text":"entertaining the notion of a contested convention .","depth":6},{"id":124,"text":"An earlier version stated only","depth":4},{"id":125,"text":"that Cruz was insisting","depth":5},{"id":126,"text":"he would win enough delegates","depth":6},{"id":127,"text":"to clinch the GOP nomination before the party 's convention in July .","depth":6}],"relations":[{"parent":255,"left":0,"right":254,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":254,"left":246,"right":253,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":246,"left":239,"right":245,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":239,"left":204,"right":238,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":204,"left":143,"right":203,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":143,"left":140,"right":142,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":140,"left":138,"right":139,"relati